description:
"Gav and Bob: Sanguinala Redux"

The continuing story unfolds across multiple battlefields and quiet moments in the grim darkness of the Imperium, all bound together by one unlikely constant: Gav Smythe and the simple act of sending Sanguinala cards.

Story by the ever amazing Neal litherland
